Class LayoutDirector<P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.render.director.LayoutDirector<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - Type of the product.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class LayoutDirector<P>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    LayoutDirector produces a graphical representation of a layout of an SBMLDocument.
